PFDril - Shiny App
Hafiz Ahsan (aha2140@columbia.edu, hafizahsan@gmail.com)

What is it?

A Proof-of-Concept web app that allows you to drill down into personal financial disclosures.
Writen in Shiny/R


What can it do?
- Show a heatmap by year and Congressional candiate ID
- Show detailed transaction when a candidate is selected

How can it be extended?
- Make it connect to database and not load static csv.gz files
- Allow downloading data
- Show a scatterplot 


